statements: SELECT * FROM bioengineered_food_products;
SELECT product_name, price, popularity_score FROM bioengineered_food_products WHERE category = 'Snacks';
SELECT product_name, category FROM bioengineered_food_products WHERE price > 10.00;
SELECT * FROM bioengineered_food_products WHERE popularity_score > 0.6 ORDER BY popularity_score DESC;
SELECT product_id, product_name, category, price FROM bioengineered_food_products WHERE price < 5.00 ORDER BY price ASC;
SELECT * FROM bioengineered_food_products WHERE category = 'Snacks' ORDER BY price DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT product_name, price FROM bioengineered_food_products WHERE popularity_score > 4.5 ORDER BY popularity_score DESC
SELECT category, AVG(price) AS average_price FROM bioengineered_food_products GROUP BY category ORDER BY average_price DESC
SELECT product_name, price FROM bioengineered_food_products WHERE category = 'Beverages' AND popularity_score > 3.0 ORDER BY price
SELECT * FROM bioengineered_food_products WHERE price BETWEEN 5.0 AND 10.0 ORDER BY price
SELECT food_name, category, price FROM bioengineered_foods;
SELECT food_name, description FROM bioengineered_foods WHERE category='Snacks';
SELECT * FROM bioengineered_foods WHERE price > 20;
SELECT analysis_date, demand, preference FROM market_analysis WHERE preference='High';
SELECT food_name, price FROM bioengineered_foods ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT * FROM bioengineered_foods WHERE category = 'Fruits' ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT food_name, price FROM bioengineered_foods WHERE price > 50 AND category = 'Vegetables';
SELECT food_name, description FROM bioengineered_foods WHERE food_id IN (1, 3, 5) AND price < 20 ORDER BY food_name ASC;
SELECT b.food_name, m.analysis_date, m.demand FROM bioengineered_foods b INNER JOIN market_analysis m ON b.food_id = m.food_id WHERE m.demand > 100 ORDER BY m.analysis_date DESC;
SELECT category, COUNT(food_id) AS food_count FROM bioengineered_foods GROUP BY category HAVING food_count > 2 ORDER BY food_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM bioengineered_products WHERE product_id = 1;
SELECT product_name, price FROM bioengineered_products WHERE price < 50;
SELECT * FROM customer_preferences WHERE rating > 4 ORDER BY customer_id DESC;
SELECT analysis_date, preferred_product FROM market_analysis WHERE analysis_id = 3;
SELECT product_name, price, production_date FROM bioengineered_products ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT product_name, price FROM bioengineered_products WHERE price > 100 ORDER BY product_name DESC;

SELECT bio.product_name, pref.rating, ma.analysis_date FROM bioengineered_products as bio JOIN customer_preferences as pref ON bio.product_id = pref.product_id JOIN market_analysis as ma ON pref.product_id = ma.analysis_id;
SELECT product_id, product_name, price, production_date FROM bioengineered_products WHERE production_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT product_name, price, expiry_date FROM bioengineered_products WHERE expiry_date < CURDATE();

SELECT bio.product_name, pref.rating, ma.analysis_date, ma.preferred_product FROM bioengineered_products as bio, customer_preferences as pref, market_analysis as ma WHERE bio.product_id = pref.product_id AND pref.product_id = ma.analysis_id ORDER BY pref.rating DESC;
SELECT * FROM FoodProducts;
SELECT product_name, price FROM FoodProducts WHERE category='Dairy' ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT id, product_name, category FROM FoodProducts WHERE production_date >= '2021-01-01';
SELECT id, product_name, price FROM FoodProducts WHERE expiration_date < '2023-01-01' AND price > 5;
SELECT COUNT(*), category FROM FoodProducts GROUP BY category ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC;
SELECT product_name, category, price FROM FoodProducts WHERE price > 50 ORDER BY category ASC
SELECT * FROM MarketTrends mt JOIN CustomerPreferences cp ON mt.product_id = cp.product_id WHERE cp.preference_score > 80 ORDER BY mt.trend_date DESC

SELECT fp.product_name, ft.demand_forecast, mt.popularity_rating FROM FoodProducts fp JOIN ForecastData ft ON fp.id = ft.product_id JOIN MarketTrends mt ON fp.id = mt.product_id WHERE ft.demand_forecast > 1000 ORDER BY mt.popularity_rating DESC
SELECT DISTINCT category FROM FoodProducts ORDER BY category

SELECT cp.customer_id, cp.preference_score, ft.demand_forecast FROM CustomerPreferences cp JOIN ForecastData ft ON cp.product_id = ft.product_id WHERE cp.preference_score > 70 ORDER BY cp.preference_score DESC
SELECT * FROM Product ORDER BY price DESC, name ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT id, name, category FROM Product WHERE quantity > 0
SELECT name, location FROM Supplier
SELECT * FROM MarketTrends WHERE date >= '2022-01-01'
SELECT product_id, projected_demand FROM DemandForecast ORDER BY date
SELECT * FROM Product WHERE price > 50 ORDER BY category DESC, name ASC
SELECT name, price, quantity FROM Product WHERE category='Electronics' ORDER BY price ASC
SELECT p.name, s.name AS supplier_name, s.location FROM Product p JOIN Supplier s ON p.id = s.id WHERE s.location='New York'
SELECT MAX(price) AS max_price, MIN(price) AS min_price, AVG(price) AS avg_price FROM Product WHERE category='Clothing'
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT product_id) AS unique_products, SUM(projected_demand) AS total_demand FROM DemandForecast WHERE date>'2022-01-01'
